Dyskador istori ha politigieth omdennys yw [[Donald Fear]] (genys Donald James Fear yn [[1962]]) hag a drig yn [[Telford]], meur y hanow drefen ev dhe vos an hweghves dhe waynyas £1,000,000 war ''[[:cy:Who Wants to Be a Millionaire?|Who Wants to Be a Millionaire?]]'' yn 2020.

==Bewnans a-varr ha resegva dyski ==
Ev yw an tressa a beswar flogh. Genys veu yn Bristol mes y deylu a removas dhe [[Manchester]] pan veu flogh yowynk. Y deylu a removas arta dhe [[Lannstefan]], [[Kernow]] pan veu degowek. [[Charles Causley]] a veu y dhyskador y'n skol gynsa, hag ena ev eth dhe [[Kolji Lannstefan|Golji Lannstefan]]. Ev a studhyas Istori ha Politigieth yn Pennskol Abertawe, le may hwrug gwaynya an Pewas Professor [[:cy:Glanmor Williams|Glanmor Williams]] rag Istori ha’n Pewas Kov John Rees. Awosa y tyskas ev yn niver a skolyow yn Telford ha [[Amwydhek]]  <ref>{{Cite web|url= https://www.shropshirestar.com/news/2012/10/13/wakeman-school-memories-sought-as-closure-looms/ |title=Wakeman School memories sought as closure looms}}</ref> kyns dos ha bos Penn Governans ha Politigieth yn Skol Ramasek Haberdashers’ Adams, Newport, [[Shropshire|Konteth Amwydhek]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.adamsgs.uk/school-life/curriculum/history |title=History Department }}</ref> Ev a omdennas wosa bos war'n dowlen.

==''Who Wants to Be a Millionaire?''==

Yn mis Gwynngala 2020 ev eth war’n dowlen bellwolok ''[[:cy:Who Wants to Be a Millionaire?||]]''. Ev o an hweghves person dhe waynyas £1,000,000 ha’n kynsa a-dhia 14 bledhen.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ukgameshows.com/ukgs/All_Time_Winners_List |title=All time winners list}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-09-11|title=Teacher beats brother to win Millionaire jackpot|language=en-GB|work=[[BBC|BBC News]]|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-54126588|access-date=2020-09-12}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|date=2020-08-20|title=Who Wants To Be A Millionaire? crowns million-pound winner - with no 'ask the audience'|url=https://inews.co.uk/news/who-wants-to-be-a-millionaire-crowns-million-pound-winner-583873|access-date=2020-09-12|website=inews.co.uk|language=en}}</ref> Y omdhyskwedhyans o arbennik drefen ev dhe dhevnydhya unn lovan sawya yn unnik hedre pub gwaynyer aral a'ga devnydhsa oll. Ev yw broder [[:cy:Davyth Fear]] neb a waynyas £500,000 an vledhen gyns.<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|date=2020-09-12|title=Who Wants to be a Millionaire? crowns first winner in 14 years|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/media/tv-radio/who-wants-be-millionaire-winner-donald-fear-itv-clarkson-b426837.html|access-date=2020-09-12|website=The Independent|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":5">{{Cite web|date=2020-09-14|title=First Who Wants To Be A Millionaire? winner in 16 years celebrated victory with caravan holiday|url=https://inews.co.uk/culture/donald-feat-who-wants-to-be-a-millionaire-winner-won-1-million-pounds-643422|access-date=2020-09-21|website=inews.co.uk|language=en}}</ref>  Heb parow yw an gwrians ma yn istori an dowlen.<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-54126588 |title=Who Wants To Be A Millionaire: Teacher beats brother to win jackpot - BBC|website=www.bbc.co.uk}}</ref> Y’n argemynnans kyns darlesa’n dowlen, y leveris Jeremy Clarkson bos Fear ‘an gwella kesstrifer yn istori an dowlen’.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-53860189 |title=Who Wants To Be A Millionaire? gets first UK jackpot winner for 14 years}}</ref>

Fear a dhevisyas ri £700,000 a’y bewas dh’y deylu, ha devnydhya £300,000 remenans rag ‘omdennans attes’ .<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":4">{{Cite web|last=Kelly|first=Helen|date=2020-09-11|title=Who Wants to be a Millionaire winner pinpoints second he knew he'd win 'A simple question'|url=https://www.express.co.uk/showbiz/tv-radio/1334566/Who-Wants-to-be-a-Millionaire-winner-Donald-final-question-answer-ITV-video|access-date=2020-09-12|website=Express.co.uk|language=en}}</ref> Wosa gwaynyas an jackpot, ev ha’y wrek eth war olyow karavan dhe Whitley Bay rag solempnya.<ref name=":5" />
Govyn £1,000,000 Fear veu 'Py unn a beswar morlader a verwis ryb arvow Karolina Gledh yn 1718?'. Ev a worthebis "Blackbeard" drefen ev dhe dhyski kors a-dro dhe morladron 8 bledhen kyns an dowlen. <ref name=":4" /><ref name=":3">{{Cite news|last=Media|first=P. A.|date=2020-09-11|title=Who Wants To Be a Millionaire? crowns first winner in 14 years|language=en-GB|work=[[The Guardian]]|url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2020/sep/11/who-wants-to-be-a-millionaire-crowns-first-winner-in-14-years|access-date=2020-09-12|issn=0261-3077}}</ref> Fear a dhegemeras omlowenheans studhyoryon skol Haberdashers' Adams.<ref name=":2" />

Yn 2022 Donald ha'y vroder Davyth a omdhiskwedhas yn para der an dowlen bellwolok "Eggheads". <ref>https://www.shropshirestar.com/entertainment/telford-entertainment/2022/02/19/telford-quizzersled-by-who-wants-to-be-a-millionaire-brothers-take-on-the-eggheads/</ref>

